      "title": "ADB provides $200 million loan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Asian Development Bank has approved a loan amount of 200 million dollars as emergency aid for Sri Lanka.",
        "These measures are aimed at improving food security and providing relief to those living in poverty - especially women and children.",
        "The Asian Development Bank has diverted the money allocated for the projects currently being carried out in this country for this loan support."
